\begin_inset Note Note
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Arises in equilibrium because supply and demand is naturally present.
 It is just at what price? To split this surplus, the cocoa producer and
 Hershey can agree to fix a price today.
 This will fully insure them against cocoa price risk (Long risk transferred
 from producer to Hershey.
 Short risk is transferred from Hershey to producer.).
\end_layout

\end_inset


