Typically, no money is exchanged when the contract is initiated.
 Contracts are usually cash-settled on the expiration date.
\begin_inset Note Note
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
It is a fair trade between consenting parties.
 Not physically settled.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

