\begin_inset Formula $S_{1}$
\end_inset

 is unbounded above, the minimum payoff to the short party is 
\begin_inset Formula $-\infty$
\end_inset

.
 The maximum payoff is 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{0,1}-0=2,750$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset


